Aegir Styra
==============

This is the source code for Aegir Styra, developed in C++ using the Irrlicht 3d library.


To compile
----------

For Windows, Visual Studio 2017 (or greater) and Code::Blocks are used 
and tested. Project files for both are in the src folder.

For Linux and macOS, CMake is used. Please see the instructions in 
src/CompilingLinuxAndMac.txt 

